<title>BELGIUM: EU clears TRW buy of Magna Automotive.</title>
<headline>EU clears TRW buy of Magna Automotive.</headline>
<dateline>BRUSSELS 1997-01-29</dateline>
<text>
<p>The European Commission has cleared the acquisition of Magna Automotive Holding GmbH, a German maker of steering wheels and airbag systems, by TRW Inc of the United States, a Commission source said on Wednesday.  </p>
<p>The deal also gives TRW control of MST Automotive GmbH and Temic Bayern-Chemie Airbag GmbH.</p>
<p>A formal announcement is expected later on Wednesday.</p>
